title: Conference Championship Preview: YOU people!!
itunes:title: Conference Championship Preview: YOU people!!
description:
A room filled with heroes- Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Gregg Rosenthal & Chris Wesseling- preview the upcoming Conference Championship games, including the potential end of the road for the Jaguars (7:30); Is Tom Brady’s injury more severe than the team is letting on? (16:00); The heroes give their picks for the Jags-Pats game (27:00); Marc is pressured into a last-minute Lock of the Week pick (31:00); Picks for the Vikings-Eagles matchup (50:00); And a triple-double Lock of the Week? (52:00);

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
